@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### Root status
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Device command (read relay state)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/device/command
Accept: application/json

### Set relay ON
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "relay": 1
}

### Set relay OFF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "relay": 0
}

### Invalid relay (validation test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/relay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "relay": 2
}

### Send telemetry
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/device/telemetry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "esp32-test-01",
  "relay": 0,
  "sensor_mock": 123,
  "temperature_c": 24.5,
  "humidity": 51
}

### Root status after telemetry
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json
